# Privacy Policy

This extension collects user-selected job description text and optional user-provided input (e.g., job title, name) solely for the purpose of generating a personalized cover letter.

The collected data is temporarily sent to a secure backend server and is not stored, shared, or used for any purpose other than generating the cover letter.

We do not collect personal identifiers, login information, or browsing activity.

No third-party tracking is used.

By using this extension, you consent to the processing of the data you provide for cover letter generation.

If you have any questions, contact us at david.schwartzman@hotmail.com
